title: Elon, SuperMega vs. Dad, Beans On Toast - H3TV #33
description: Today we discuss the next chapter for Twitter after being purchased by The Musk, along with an update to the beans on toast debacle, a call with Dad (Nathan Barnett) & Matt Watson to discuss their heated boxing match coming up, & much more!
